
Minecraft custom tools for SliTaz GNU/Linux. Tazcraft can install and run Minecraft server
as well as getting the client and starting to play. It can also optionaly install the Java
Runtime Environement (JRE)


Server configuration
--------------------
Config file: server.properties

gamemode=
	0 - Survival
	1 - Creative
	2 - Adventure
	3 - Spectator
